issue.title: Add Leaderboards
issue.body:
We can add leaderboards to each level or the entire game to track the high score.

The groundwork for a full-game leaderboard was started in [this commit](58f743a23ac0834c79679a0ac22b71696fb63918).

issue.title: Add Minimum Score Thresholds to Reach the Next Level
issue.body:
Instead of allowing the user to continue to the next level after only finishing the current level, we should require the user obtain a certain score before they can move to the next level.

We may need to update how scoring works i.e. punishing the player less for misses.

issue.title: Fix Refuse Throwing Bug
issue.body: We want to prevent the user from being able to drag items directly into the bins. We should try to setup a drag radius the user cannot move the refuse object outside of.

issue.title: Fix UI Scaling Issues
issue.body: Update the game to work well on multiple screen sizes
